	<h1 class="title">不知道吧，雅虎CEO还往全美最大派对上砸钱了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Vanessa Friedman</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-06 14:28:57 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9245/medium/9245.jpg?1436687254" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


